Another image I had was of the 1981 movie that to everyone surprise,even shock,won academy awards for BEST PICTURE, BEST MUSIC, BEST COSTUMES, BEST FILM AND MORE …Chariots of Fire!
I thought of the scene where Eric liddle was discussing his running and he says …”when I run I feel the pleasure and glory of God.” As for the rain…tears of God for all the dead!!
